28986", "video": {"preview": "https://pbs.twimg.com/amplify_video_thumb/2054307086972878848/img/8O4HMH-6HEg-Vfbe.jpg", "mpeg": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2054307086972878848/pl/wQTcl5tsTYJEBkNe.m3u8?v=e36", "aspectRatio": [9, 16], "heightRatio": 177, "type": "video/mp4", "url": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2054307086972878848/vid/avc1/320x568/feas9dybD1-O2BNh.mp4"}, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1863842853484376064/Jxjw6pIS_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Scott Jennings", "username": "ScottJenningsKY"}, "content": "This New York Times \"article\" about Israel is such a journalistic atrocity that I actually feel stupid reading it out loud.\n\nIf everyone at the NYT who is responsible for this is not fired, then the publication will lose whatever shred of credibility it has left.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 15501}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsPoFmcw", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 41, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8615426, "raw_content": "In the Decades between 1980 and 2000, Arcadia had practically zero 'Asians' in their Demographic...too low to even provide a percentage in the Census.\n\nArcadia CA in 1980 had 88.50% White and 6.86% Hispanic with practically fractional representation of any other demographic group.\n\nBy 2000 the White population shrank to 40.07%, the Hispanic population grew slightly to 10.61%...and suddenly there were 24,018 'Asian' inhabitants making up 45.37% of the Population.\n\nBy 2020 17.59% of the Population was White, 13.06% Hispanic and a WHOPPING 64.59% were Asian.\n\nSOURCES:\n\nhttps://www2.census.gov/prod2/decennial/documents/1980a_caCs1-01.pdf\n\nhttps://www2.census.gov/library/publications/decennial/1990/cp-1/cp-1-6-1.pdf\n\nhttps://data.census.gov/table/DECENNIALSF12000.P004?g=160XX00US0602462\n\nhttps://data.census.gov/table/DECENNIALPL2020.P2?q=p2&g=160XX00US0602462\n\n", "author": "Moebius", "created": 1778671016386, "profile_picture": "0F9hm63l5dUw", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "VaporJet11", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Arcadia California is Compromised...Nest of CCP Spies.  No Wonder They Could 'Elect' a CHICOM Spy as Mayor...and the U.S. Representative for Arcadia is Judy Chu (D) who represents California's 28th Congressional District. ", "last_comment_created": 1778680190285, "content": "<p>In the Decades between 1980 and 2000, Arcadia had practically zero 'Asians' in their Demographic...too low to even provide a percentage in the Census.</p>\n<p>Arcadia CA in 1980 had 88.50% White and 6.86% Hispanic with practically fractional representation of any other demographic group.</p>\n<p>By 2000 the White population shrank to 40.07%, the Hispanic population grew slightly to 10.61%...and suddenly there were 24,018 'Asian' inhabitants making up 45.37% of the Population.</p>\n<p>By 2020 17.59% of the Population was White, 13.06% Hispanic and a WHOPPING 64.59% were Asian.</p>\n<p>SOURCES:</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www2.census.gov/prod2/decennial/documents/1980a_caCs1-01.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.census.gov/prod2/decennial/documents/1980a_caCs1-01.pdf</a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www2.census.gov/library/publications/decennial/1990/cp-1/cp-1-6-1.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.census.gov/library/publications/decennial/1990/cp-1/cp-1-6-1.pdf</a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://data.census.gov/table/DECENNIALSF12000.P004?g=160XX00US0602462\" target=\"_blank\">https://data.census.gov/table/DECENNIALSF12000.P004?g=160XX00US0602462</a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://data.census.gov/table/DECENNIALPL2020.P2?q=p2&amp;g=160XX00US0602462\" target=\"_blank\">https://data.census.gov/table/DECENNIALPL2020.P2?q=p2&amp;g=160XX00US0602462</a></p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 2, "score_up": 41, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsPn8lLk", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 201, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "pence", "id": 8614920, "raw_content": "", "author": "CleanUpPhillyTrump24", "created": 1778638776945, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "SalteenCracker", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsPn8lLk.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/hF0kEQ1Rpu9S.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/pSyHaYGYmDLReju6.jpeg", "width": 768, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 768}], "blurhash": "UGIz#Q^jE3s8nra*s*Rl8wrWNKxt}u#mNHof", "full_resolution": [942, 942]}, "title": "THUNE THE GOON OUT BY JUNE ", "last_comment_created": 1778640979317, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 1, "score_up": 201, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "\u2728\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0MEME MAGIC\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u2728", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "20542754172